name: Your Worth, not Your Weight
description:
Psst... let me tell you a little secret: each body has the same value, each body is beautiful, each body is a temple. Your weight does not define your worth. Don’t let anyone tell you a different story. You are beautiful just the way you are!

- This is a message from Rebel Berries. You are not alone. For personal non-commercial use. Find us on Instagram and Twitter: @rebelberries
